main.value: Apache Commons CLI provides a simple API for presenting, processing and validating a command line interface.
The Apache Commons IO library contains utility classes, stream implementations, file filters,file comparators, endian transformation classes, and much more.
A library that supports gettext-based internationalization        (i18n) of Java applications.
